Invocation Name: animal sounds
des:
This skill plays an animal sound when asked. 75+ animals and hundreds of different sounds are available. 
You can ask to hear a specific animal, or ask Animal Sounds for a random animal. Each animal may have several sound clips, so you can hear something new each time you ask!

Some of the animals available are listed below. More are added often, so come back to see what's new!
